OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FA cellmate of a prisoner who died from
OL,7,Fa spice overdose at HMP Parc did not
OL,8,Falert staff because he believed
OL,9,Fnothing would be done about it, an
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FRoss Andrew Appleby, 29, died 18
OL,13,FJanuary 2023. He had been remanded at
OL,14,Fthe prison on 13 October 2022 and was
OL,15,Fsentenced to a three year jail term
OL,16,Ffor drug dealing offences.
