OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest, at Pontypridd Coroners
OL,7,FCourt, heard from Jerome Winter, who
OL,8,Fshared a cell with Mr Appleby, for
OL,9,Fabout a month before his death on 18
OL,10,FJanuary 2023.
OL,12,FMr Winter described him as a "good
OL,13,Fguy, kind of popular" on the wing.
OL,15,FWearing a black tracksuit in the
OL,16,Fwitness stand, he said Mr Appleby
OL,17,Fwould use the drug known as spice
OL,18,F"sometimes" but "not everyday",
OL,19,Fsmoking it on a tool known as a 'bong'
OL,20,Fmade from a toilet roll and a vape.
