OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Mr Appleby began to
OL,7,Fsmoke spice just before 9pm on the
OL,8,Fnight of his death.
OL,10,FJerome Winter told the court he
OL,11,Fencouraged his cellmate not to take
OL,12,Fthe drug, and to instead stay up and
OL,13,Fwatch television - but Mr Appleby
OL,14,Fcontinued smoking.
OL,16,FJust before 11pm, Mr Winter said Ross
OL,17,FAppleby was slumped over in bed with
OL,18,Fhis head by his feet.
