OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe told the inquest he began to move
OL,7,Fhim into a more comfortable position
OL,8,Fand noticed his face was "blue" and
OL,9,Fhands were "freezing" to the touch. He
OL,10,Fdescribed realising there was vomit on
OL,11,FMr Appleby's pillow and in his mouth.
OL,13,FTalking to a neighbouring cell to tell
OL,14,Fthem he thought Mr Appleby was dead,
OL,15,FMr Winter said his neighbours told him
OL,16,Fraise the alarm, and described prison
OL,17,Fstaff attending the cell in "less than
OL,18,Fa minute."
