OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FOn Monday, the inquest heard how Mr
OL,7,FAppleby had a history of drug use,
OL,8,Fincluding suffering from possible drug
OL,9,Finduced atrial fibrillation - a type
OL,10,Fof heart rhythm problem. He also
OL,11,Fsuffered from benzodiazepine poisoning
OL,12,Fat the age of 19.
OL,14,FA HMP Parc Health Care Assistant,
OL,15,FJoanne Kite, told the coroner's court
OL,16,Fshe wasn't aware of Ross' history of a
OL,17,Fdrug induced atrial fibrillation on
OL,18,Fconducting his initial health care
OL,19,Fassessment.
