OL,3,C'Lack of action over spice use' at HMP
OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FHMP Parc Prison GP Dr Rosemary Marnell
OL,7,Fsaid Ross never reported symptoms of
OL,8,Fatrial fibrillation whilst at HMP Parc.
OL,10,FThe court also heard evidence from the
OL,11,Fprison officer who attended Mr
OL,12,FAppleby's cell the night he died.
OL,14,FBal Rai, a prison officer at Parc
OL,15,FPrison since 2009, said he was not
OL,16,Ffamiliar with Ross Appleby before the
OL,17,Fnight of his death. He added that
OL,18,Fthere was no mention of him in the day
OL,19,Fstaff's handover.
