OL,4,CParc, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe court was also given a timeline
OL,7,Ffrom Ian Sayt, who was working in the
OL,8,Fcontrol room that night. He said the
OL,9,Fdoor to Mr Appleby's cell was unlocked
OL,10,Fjust before 11 PM.
OL,12,FAt 11:19 PM, first responders arrived;
OL,13,Fat 11:25 PM, two ambulances arrived;
OL,14,Fat 11:30 PM, a third ambulance
OL,15,Farrived; and an air ambulance doctor
OL,16,Farrived at 11:45 PM.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
